'''Chamarel FC''' is a [[Mauritius|Mauritian]] [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Bambous, Mauritius|Bambous]]. They play in the [[Mauritian League]], the top division in Mauritian football.<ref name="soccerway">{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/teams/mauritius/chamarel/24978/matches/|title=Mauritius&nbsp;– Chamarel FC&nbsp;– Risultati e calendario&nbsp;– Soccerway|publisher=it.soccerway.com|accessdate=2014-02-22}}</ref>

==Stadium==
Their home stadium is [[Stade Germain Comarmond]] (cap. 5,000), located in [[Bambous, Mauritius|Bambous]].

